Written by this darius nash?

00:26.752 --> 00:29.386
What an insidious way
this man has.

00:29.388 --> 00:30.687
You're hired.
There's something that you.

00:30.689 --> 00:32.622
Should know before
you pull that trigger.

00:32.624 --> 00:34.391
Full disclosure... I'm gay.

00:34.393 --> 00:35.926
That's no problem.

00:35.928 --> 00:38.862
Daddy, I need your help.

00:38.864 --> 00:42.482
You know I never could deny you.

00:42.484 --> 00:43.984
What do you need?

00:46.271 --> 00:47.871
You. What are you doing?

00:47.873 --> 00:49.606
