my business, you hear me?

00:49.608 --> 00:50.707
I was trying to help.

00:50.709 --> 00:52.476
I told you
he was not the problem.

00:52.478 --> 00:56.179
Kevin, I have no idea what is
going on with the two of you.

00:56.181 --> 00:57.647
Charity, I've been doing
some research.

00:57.649 --> 00:58.915
About what?

00:58.917 --> 01:00.317
What I've been struggling with.

01:00.319 --> 01:01.768
You are what you are.

01:01.770 --> 01:03.186
You can't change that.

01:09.762 --> 01:11.561
We were up with that baby
all night?

01:11.563 --> 01:13.330
You know he's still
struggling with that rash,

01:13.332 --> 01:15.665
But he'll be fine.

01:15.667 --> 01:19.419
We had a long
and wonderful conversation.

01:19.421 --> 01:20.871
Jacob scheduled the movers.

01:20.873 --> 01:22.222
That's a shame.

01:22.224 --> 01:24.274
I was looking forward
to watching him carry.

01:24.276 --> 01:26.359
All that furniture
we bought him across town,

01:26.361 --> 01:27.994
Piece by ill-gotten piece.

01:27.996 --> 01:31.748
When are you gonna tell him
who basie skanks really is?

01:31.750 --> 01:34.251
If you tell him,
he'll stay, james.

01:34.253 --> 01:36.169
I'm not even sure it's true.

01:36.171 --> 01:39.089
As I recall,
darrell had two daughters,

01:39.091 --> 01:40.323
And that was it.

01:40.325 --> 01:42.359
Do you remember any boys
in that family?

01:42.361 --> 01:43.643
No.

01:43.645 --> 01:44.861
But men have been known.

01:44.863 --> 01:47.164
To let their seed
fly on the wind,

01:47.166 --> 01:50.834
Desiring for fields
not their own.

01:50.836 --> 01:52.002
I'll talk to him about it.

01:52.004 --> 01:54.788
Thank you.

01:54.790 --> 01:56.590
But I won't beg him to stay.

01:56.592 --> 01:59.009
Far be it from me to ask you
to scuff your pride.

01:59.011 --> 02:00.143
In the name of something.

02:00.145 --> 02:02.963
As small and worthless as love.

02:02.965 --> 02:04.014
Come here. What?

02:04.016 --> 02:05.348
What?

02:07.953 --> 02:09.919
Baby.

02:09.922 --> 02:13.290
What?

02:13.292 --> 02:16.560
Hey!

02:16.562 --> 02:18.645
