"Hey, isaiah.
It's your girl, sophia.

03:05.360 --> 03:07.677
Was wondering about
your relationship situation."

03:07.679 --> 03:08.778
Stop!

03:10.649 --> 03:12.115
I just don't want to
seem desperate.

03:12.117 --> 03:13.884
But you are.

03:13.886 --> 03:15.218
I'm kidding, I'm kidding.

03:15.220 --> 03:20.140
You know, isaiah rehearses
every saturday at triumph.

03:20.142 --> 03:22.459
We could go.

03:22.461 --> 03:23.877
That wouldn't be weird?

03:23.879 --> 03:27.030
It would.

03:27.032 --> 03:29.766
How long you been here?

03:29.768 --> 03:32.385
I couldn't sleep.

03:32.387 --> 03:34.037
Go get ready for school.

03:35.374 --> 03:38.775
Do you want to be
bae goals 2017 or not?

03:38.777 --> 03:41.845
Closed mouths don't get fed.

03:41.847 --> 03:44.681
Hey, she's gonna miss me.
You know, when I'm gone?

03:44.683 --> 03:48.018
I'm not arguing with you.

03:48.020 --> 03:50.503
Isaiah hambrick?

03:50.505 --> 03:52.038
Eavesdropping's a sin, you know.

03:53.392 --> 03:56.559
Why didn't you come down?

03:56.561 --> 03:58.178
Because I wasn't
in the mood for another one.

03:58.180 --> 03:59.613
Of my father's paranoid

03:59.615 --> 04:01.414
"basie skanks is out
to get me" speeches.

04:01.416 --> 04:04.134
There you go.

04:04.136 --> 04:06.403
That being said,
I need to talk to basie.

04:06.405 --> 04:08.254
About that foolishness
he pulled last week.

04:08.256 --> 04:11.458
He should've told us
he was giving me that church.

04:11.460 --> 04:13.460
Definitely not making
my life any easier.

04:15.380 --> 04:17.529
Wait a minute, pastor.

04:17.531 --> 04:19.916
There you go.

04:20.986 --> 04:21.952
Yeah?

04:21.954 --> 04:23.086
Yeah.

04:25.424 --> 04:26.957
Okay.

04:26.959 --> 04:28.558
Can't wait to get out of here.

04:28.560 --> 04:30.860
Tasha's finally showing me
the parsonage this afternoon,

04:30.862 --> 04:32.996
So we could be out of here
as soon as next week.

04:33.465 --> 04:34.698
Mwah.

04:38.971 --> 04:41.037
Pastor greenleaf.

04:41.039 --> 04:42.172
Bishop's ring cleared, scoop.

04:42.174 --> 04:43.807
Story's over. No comment.

04:43.809 --> 04:45.291
I'm not here for the paper.

04:45.293 --> 04:47.527
That's a nice try.

04:47.529 --> 04:50.413
I thought you might want to go
on a post-scandal date.

04:50.415 --> 04:52.498
Yeah, to celebrate.

04:52.500 --> 04:53.783
You know, whoever told you
you were funny.

04:53.785 --> 04:55.285
Did the world
a great disservice.

04:55.287 --> 04:57.320
I'm serious.

04:57.322 --> 05:00.390
Look, I'll be off the clock.

05:00.392 --> 05:01.524
Is that really possible?

05:01.526 --> 05:04.995
I give you my word
as a christian.

05:04.997 --> 05:07.697
Mr. Nash, I'm flattered.

05:07.699 --> 05:09.165
No.

05:09.167 --> 05:13.269
Okay.

05:13.271 --> 05:15.221
If you change your mind.

05:20.779 --> 05:23.113
And it's darius.

05:23.115 --> 05:25.331
Good morning, pastor.
Morning, darlene.

05:34.960 --> 05:38.595
Have we heard back yet from
that girl at hallelujah 95.7?

05:38.597 --> 05:41.231
The one who finds you
so terribly transformative?

05:41.233 --> 05:42.365
I have, actually.

05:42.367 --> 05:44.751
And?

05:44.753 --> 05:46.436
She's having me
come in next week.

05:46.438 --> 05:48.104
To do an interview with mike o.

05:48.106 --> 05:49.906
Well, be sure
to give him my best.

05:49.908 --> 05:53.226
Outside of the lord,
mae, I assure you,

05:53.228 --> 05:54.778
You will be my main theme.

05:54.780 --> 05:57.080
You rang, mama?

05:57.082 --> 05:59.716
What is that thing?

05:59.718 --> 06:01.117
It's mama's way
of saying "come,".

06:01.119 --> 06:03.203
In lieu of a dog whistle
or a chain.

06:03.205 --> 06:05.722
It bestows a certain
poetry upon something.

06:05.724 --> 06:08.391
Which might otherwise
be merely mechanical.

06:08.393 --> 06:10.226
And it saves me from listening.

06:10.228 --> 06:12.662
To that interminable
voice message on her phone.

06:12.664 --> 06:14.030
What can I do for you, mama?

06:14.032 --> 06:16.766
We want you to fire carlton.

06:16.768 --> 06:19.719
Because betty wilcox has
an issue with gay marriage? No.

06:19.721 --> 06:22.205
No, this is about
more than betty wilcox.

06:22.207 --> 06:25.675
Over half the deacon board
haven't even pledged yet.

06:25.677 --> 06:27.844
And his brazenness
causes concern.

06:27.846 --> 06:29.062
For many of our other members.

06:29.064 --> 06:30.880
Says who? Betty wilcox?

06:30.882 --> 06:32.382
Says half the deacon board.

06:32.384 --> 06:34.134
Then they should
go somewhere else.

06:34.136 --> 06:35.969
Well, that's the problem...
They will.

06:35.971 --> 06:37.987
Are you okay with this?

06:37.989 --> 06:39.672
I can't lose half
the deacon board.

06:39.674 --> 06:41.374
Over a choir director.

06:41.376 --> 06:42.826
Wasn't he fired
from another church?

06:42.828 --> 06:44.394
Two churches. And he sued them.

06:44.396 --> 06:46.312
And he lost.

06:46.314 --> 06:47.597
I won't do it.

06:47.599 --> 06:48.631
Gigi...

06:48.633 --> 06:50.116
Who's gonna direct the choirs?

06:50.118 --> 06:52.035
I will not debate this with you.

06:52.037 --> 06:54.003
You are the associate pastor.

06:54.005 --> 06:56.906
Now, are you going to fire him,
or do I have to do it?

07:01.129 --> 07:04.564
I'll take care of it.

07:04.566 --> 07:06.316
And do it soon, please.

07:06.318 --> 07:07.917
Betty's leaving town
for new orleans.

07:07.919 --> 07:09.886
To see that granddaughter
that you baptized,

07:09.888 --> 07:11.287
And I don't want
her leaving here.

07:11.289 --> 07:12.922
Without writing us a check.

