Thank you.

08:41.712 --> 08:43.279
What's good, pastor greenleaf?

08:43.280 --> 08:44.447
Yeah, so, just real quick...

08:44.449 --> 08:46.216
No, for you,
I got nothing but time.

08:46.218 --> 08:47.917
I met with the g.C., all right?

08:47.919 --> 08:49.936
They're gonna start digging
the foundation this week.

08:49.938 --> 08:51.387
I'm also putting together
a packet of.

